MAIN CHARACTER: Som

Name: “S” (Placeholder)
Age: 28
Born: //2003
Background:
Bangladeshi civil engineer working at a Japanese engineering firm in Dhaka. Specializes in structural design, load calculations, and CAD drawings. Wanted to pursue environmental engineering but gave up due to job insecurity.
Gets scolded by boss on the first chapters for missing few dimension and calculations

Personality:
Confident at home, awkward and misunderstood at work, logical but distrustful post-outbreak. Lies unconsciously, smirks when proven right, avoids arguments unless it's personal. Knows about lot of things yet master of none of it mainly due to his personality that can't stand still at one thing and learns various things at once which makes him knowledgeable about many things but not to the of someone who works on that certain thing.

Becomes stoic and cold after incident zero and very indecisive but calculative and a purpose.

Languages:
Fluent in Bangla and English; understands basic Japanese (anime and work exposure).

Appearance & Traits:
Greying hair linked to past trauma, tech-savvy gamer who wears glasses.
Height 5'11
Weight: 72 kg
Build: mesopomorh but not very muscular due to him not working out.

Likes: Gacha games, mystery and thriller Anime, his mom, Anne's music and hair.

Dislikes: ????

His relation to the world of Another sky:
It seems like he strangely and weirdly got transferred to the world of Another sky on March 31st.
He didn't realized that he wasn't on his own world when his mother mentions WW3 which made his blood run cold And naBecause there is no ww3 from the world he's form.


