The first to disappear:
Anne: Ex Filipina girlfriend they meet over online chat and dated for 6 years long distance
, artist, dancer, singer. Working in local political group as she wants to reach higher in social structure to fix the corruption she has been seeing since childhood. Broke up with S because she wants to focus on her goals but still likes S and hopes to be with him when everything settles down on her end but S doesn't understands that part of her and they sometimes argue about it on messengers. Anne wants S to wait and focus on himself and build himself up and Anne wants to focus on her goals so she can make herself better for herself, family and to stand next to him when she can prove herself. Suddenly disappeared from face of the world when S got transfered to Another Sky's world as if she never existed. Every picture of her disappeared from S's phone and hard drives spiraling him into internal crisis and her face calmed him during his toughest days.

After getting transfered to The world of Another sky S couldn't find anything of her. All the images and conversation seemed to have disappeared with her

Eight others who vanished from photos and memories.
4 guys and 3 girls excluding Anne
whom he can't remember the face of but they did existed in his life and were every important to him.

