Anomaly in the world :
RAIN OF OBSEIDA

Deep black rainfall starts globally two weeks after the outbreak.

Purpose remains unknown.

Also called Black Rain, Moon Rain, Starfall depending on region.

Becomes a daily thing after first few things and people aren't scared of it
Shows the adaptability of humans.
Some people says the infected becomes clam and still when the black rain falls on em.

Some underground scientist who tested the black rain says it's properties are no different from normal rain but has acidic materials in it. Which is harmless to humans. Further tested is needed for full details of this rain.
Some believe this rain would have happened either way even if the outbreaks didn't happen.
When the rain starts the sky start looking like it's bleeding down literally.
The sky becomes all gooey and dark.
It almost blocks out the sun which makes everything dark like nighttime.

Some meteorologist theorise the rain would have happened either way with or without the outbreak. Hinting it could be some kind of cosmic or natural phenomena and was gonna happen either way.

Fog of medusa:

This fog only appeared in Germany so much into the story
A yellowish fog that kills and suffocate anything except zombies.
Even infected dies if they are in the fog.

The global chilling:
Started happening 2 months into the outbreaks
Seems like the planet stated cooling down a bit by bit. There's at least 5-6 times a month there will be hailing worldwide.
It becomes worse when black rain and hailing happens together. Worse time to be outside.

The great migration:

Trillions of ants and other insects started going somewhere in the North. Are they running.

The birds and some wild animals also moving towards there.

