🧬 INFECTED (6 Types)

Type-1
"They think"

These infected are able to think and act like normal humans which makes them dangerous as they can try to fight and take out human bases

Type-2
"They talk"

These infected act and talk like normal human which helps them to blend into human crowds and underground bunker and their bite can turn human into zombies or infected
They seems to be enjoying when killing their prey

Type -3
"They trick"
These. Infected trick human by faking the voice of their loved ones
Their body looks like a skinwalker and they mostly out at evening to dawn

Type-4
"They take"

These infected kidnaps human during their sleep and tear away human body with their hands and enjoy eating while the human is still alive
They especially love eating human kids.

Type - 5
"Glitch"
Unknown type
Extremely dangerous
It seems like they flicker between realities as their body twitch and turn extremely fast. It's like the pathogens or virus or whatever they are affected by has full control of the body and using it without restrictions

Traits common in every infected:
Retain partial intelligence roughly equivalent to 6–8 year-old children.

Avoid familiar humans but attack strangers.

Whisper unknown phrases.

Eyes reflect light like cats.

Bite marks heal with black, bloated tissue.

Blend into human groups.

Possibly caused by a prion disease (unconfirmed theory).


