🧟‍♀️ GHUULS

Created when bitten by both a zombie and an infected.
Extremely rare as the body usually cannot handle two things at once.
Seems like only a strong willed person can be fully turned into a ghuuls(just a theory) as nor a single alive specimen was caught since they're highly agile like they're teleporting. And kill out entire base in mere seconds as survivors doesn't know what's happening.
Ghuuls are extremely pale white from body to hair and hair sometimes turn into brown whenever they walk in Rain of Obsedia. They seems to enjoy walking in rain like they become human and went back to their childhood playing in rain.
But it stops the moment the rain stops and they go back to their destruction
As for why they going around killing it's unknown

First Ghuul is S’s mother — Incident Zero.

Body turns pure white; eyes flicker between brown and black.

Glitches between realities.

Strongest threat known.

Retains some emotions; notably ran away instead of harming S.
But ends up destroying other survival houses and camps
Secretly watched S from afar.

Her transformation occurs two weeks post-outbreak after a deeply developed bond with S. Happens when S goes out on a supply run leaving his mom in the barricaded house but...

Drives S’s global quest for truth.

There are other known Ghuuls which started appearing few months into the story. Most of em look normal human until you look at their distorted face.
Some ghuuls even have their back cracked open but the flesh looks like a thread trying to hold itself together.

There are currently 173 known Ghuuls around the world. They're reported and being constantly updated because of their extremely dangerous nature and hard to kill as shooting the brain doesn't stops it.

"What does stop it then?" A drifter says-


